    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    v0 = 0.69
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.09)))
    v0 = ((v2 * wp.cos(tmp + 0.38)) * ((v1 + 0.36 - v0 + 0.31) * wp.sin(v2 + 0.97)))
    v1 = wp.abs(0.78)
    tmp = (0.77 + ((v0 + 0.65 * tmp + 0.84) * (v2 + 0.48 + v2 + 0.59)))
    v0 = v1
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.16) + (tmp + 0.39 + v1 + 0.56)) + ((v1 + 0.88 + v1 + 0.10) / v1))
    data[tid] = v0
